Russia RTS Stock-Index Futures Gain at Start of Trading

-- B y   H a l i a   P a v l i v a
-- 
2011-04-11T15:10:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-11/russia-rts-stock-index-futures-gain-at-start-of-trading.html
Russia ’s RTS stock-index futures
expiring in June gained less than 0.1 percent to 206,460 by
11:06 a.m. in  New York .  Contracts on OAO Lukoil, the country’s second-biggest oil
producer, OAO Sberbank, Russia’s largest lender, and OAO
Gazprom, the natural-gas export monopoly, were little changed.
The Market Vectors Russia ETF, a U.S.-traded fund that holds
Russian shares, fell 0.8 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Halia Pavliva in New York at 
 hpavliva@bloomberg.net   To contact the editors responsible for this story:
